name: v5.109.0
body:
## What's Changed
* chore(deps): bump axios from 1.11.0 to 1.12.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/616
* Update module resolution and datadog-ci by @avangelillo in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/618
* Add dependabot upgrade workflow by @avangelillo in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/617
* chore(deps-dev): bump ts-jest from 29.4.0 to 29.4.4 in the all-minor-and-patch-updates group by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/619
* chore(deps-dev): bump @types/serverless from 1.78.34 to 3.12.27 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/623
* chore(deps-dev): bump jest-environment-node from 26.6.2 to 30.2.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/620
* chore(deps-dev): bump typescript from 4.9.5 to 5.9.3 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/622
* [CHORE] use builtin fetch by @ava-silver in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/624
* chore(deps-dev): bump prettier from 2.8.8 to 3.6.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/626

## New Contributors
* @ava-silver made her first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/serverless-plugin-datadog/pull/624
